HEADWORD: konini
<hw>konini</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>An erect deciduous shrub or tree
(<spn>Fuchsia excorticata</spn>), native to New Zealand, growing up to
10 feet, with maroon-flushed flowers.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> tree fuchsia, native fuchsia, <spn>Fuchsia
excorticata</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

